data.description: Spacious four-bedroom, two-story home in an amazing area that’s close to shopping, schools and parks. Modern amenities, all new flooring on main level with LVP, gorgeous fireplace and lots natural light, and a well-designed floor plan. Enjoy the privacy of a fenced-in yard, perfect for outdoor activities and pets. This home is hard to find with large bedrooms, formal dining and a wonderful rec room area in the lower level that’s perfect for game night.
